{"tid":1547751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日大嶼山壓力測試","createTime":"2019-09-06T18:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T18:47:38.000Z","uid":252258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70739d3d6f163ee497fd9258456c924f66edb181","tid":1547751,"uid":252258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JA2rvfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJA2rvfZ.jpg&h=e8bf70ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得聽日就算點樣都最好唔好坐機場快線出返嚟市區<br />\n因為佢得兩個站 : 機場同香港站<br />\n<br />\n如果大嶼山發生咗啲咩事, 而又坐咗機場快線<br />\n係冇得走嘅<br />\n<br />\n佢哋唔會蠢到香港站唔放部署喺度吧<br />\n<br />\n就算冇嘅, 格車出緊嚟嗰時調派都可以好快去到啦<br />\n<br />\n所以, 有啲咩事萬大事都係坐東涌線好啲!!!<br />\n(Or 其他方法)<br />\n<br />\n*雖然我知我仲係P牌仔, 人微言輕<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到, 唔想再見到有手足被捕!!<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不分化"},{"pid":"aa90325061580eb2c56aecc1a58f7d65029cd504","tid":1547751,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"048d175d3fd39b81f56ce593126838e9365bb6a2","tid":1547751,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:47:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}